title: The Beautiful Lie S01E01 PDTV.XviD-AUTeam.avi
description:
A grand, complex love story of love, lust and betrayal across three families and generations, The Beautiful Lie is a contemporary re-imagining of Leo Tolstoy's classic novel and one of the greatest ever relationship dramas, Anna Karenina.

CAST: Sarah Snook, Benedict Samuel




The Beautiful Lie - Series 1, Episode 1



Anna Ivin flies home from a family holiday to help save her brother's marriage. At the airport, Anna is introduced by chance to Skeet. They fall into an instant and helpless attraction.



Original Air Date: 18-Oct-2015
